{
  "texts": [
    "We invite collaboration from educators, developers, and HCI researchers to test, extend, and adapt this framework.",
    "If effective, it could offer a scalable model for responsible LLM use in education, coding bootcamps, and even industry settings, where correctness and clarity are paramount, but LLM output remains opaque.",
    "Going forward, our immediate next steps involve implementing the experimental framework outlined here.",
    "This experiment will test our core hypotheses and provide insights into the effectiveness of combining TDD with LLM-based code and spreadsheet generation.",
    "The study will establish clear benchmarks and success indicators through structured tasks, pre/post analysis, and reflective feedback."
  ]
}